OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fwarm and sunny evening then a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some clear spells, and a
OL,8,Flittle cloud at times. Winds will
OL,9,Fremain light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA dry and bright morning and
OL,12,Fbecoming hot again inland. Cloud
OL,13,Fincreasing through the afternoon with
OL,14,Fsome heavy showers developing, merging
OL,15,Fto longer spells of thundery rain
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
